data.description: BEE-U-TEE-FUL Home in sought-after MARLEY PARK community!  This original home owner did not skimp on the upgrades, and they even added some post-construction.  Walk up to the home in a park-like setting with tons of mature trees and pass through the custom iron gate to the arched front door.  Enter into a spacious hallway with high ceilings and stylish tile flooring.Split bedrooms are in front of home.  Two secondary bedrooms on the right share a bathroom.  Generous primary bedroom is very private with lofty 12-foot ceiling, wood blinds and an upgraded en suite bathroom boasting a remodeled large, glass walk-in shower, dual sinks, and a custom closet that you must see to believe.  All three bedrooms have upgraded wood flooring.WAIT, THERE'S MORE...
